  "prompt": "Which is the best coaching in Patna for the IIT-JEE?",
  "response": "There are several well-regarded coaching institutes in Patna for IIT-JEE preparation. Some of the best options include:\n\n1. **Allen Career Institute**: Known for its comprehensive study material and experienced faculty, Allen has a strong reputation in preparing students for competitive exams.\n\n2. **Aakash Institute**: Aakash is famous for its structured programs and extensive coaching for various entrance exams, including IIT-JEE.\n\n3. **Resonance**: With a good track record in engineering entrance exam preparation, Resonance offers various courses tailored to IIT-JEE.\n\n4. **Bansal Classes**: This institute has a longstanding reputation for IIT-JEE coaching and offers specialized programs for students.\n\n5. **Motion Education**: Known for its student-centric approach and interactive sessions, Motion Education provides quality coaching for IIT-JEE aspirants.\n\n6. **Vibrant Academy**: This institute focuses on personalized attention and offers various flexible learning options.\n\nWhen selecting a coaching institute, consider factors such as faculty experience, student reviews, success rates, batch size, and the study material provided. It\u2019s also a good idea to visit the institutes, if possible, to get a feel for their environment and teaching style.",
